<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="accelerate-time-to-market">Accelerate Time to Market</h2>



<p>By using CAEPE, engineering teams reduce the time required to onboard and release new applications to end users. CAEPE allows DevOps teams to automate pipelines and manage workflows and tests, while developers and QA engineers can build deployment plans based on guided workflows and prescribed tests without relying on DevOps.</p>
